# Trivy ignore file — accepted-risk CVE allowlist.
#
# The CI image gate (.github/workflows/container-build.yml) fails on any
# vulnerability of severity UNKNOWN..CRITICAL that has a fix available
# (unfixed vulnerabilities are ignored — ignore-unfixed).
# Add a CVE ID below ONLY with a one-line justification. Every entry here is an
# explicitly accepted risk and should be revisited when upstream ships a fix.
#
# Format (one per line):
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN  # why it's accepted / upstream status
